# Register Files

A minimum of 3 register files are required for POWER:

* Floating-point
* Integer
* Control and Condition Code Registers (CR0-7, CTR, LR)
* SPRs (Special Purpose Registers)

The FP and Integer registers need to be a massive 128 x 64-bit.

